<br />
<p>For information about obtaining any of our Teaching issues, please view the <a href="school-of-law-home/academics/journals/slu-law-journal/subscribe">subscription form</a>.</p>
<p>For further inquiries about the Teaching issue, please contact <a href="mailto:ncejas@slu.edu" target="_blank">Nicolas Cejas</a>, Teaching Issue Managing Editor.</p><div id="spacer"></div>
